---

<PageLayout title="Contact Me" description="Let's connect">
    <p>
        I appreciate your interest and am looking forward to connecting with
        you. Here's how you can get in touch.
    </p>
    <p>
        Scheduling a video call a preferred way of contacting me and I would be
        happy to meet you. Feel free to drop me a line for any general
        inquiries, comments or just to say hello. I usually respond within 24
        hours.
    </p>
